codex
I caught one subtle issue before validation: Dexible’s own `computeMinFeeUnits` logic has a lossy decimal conversion for tokens below 18 decimals. The verifier should mirror the on-chain fee math exactly, not “fix” it locally, otherwise it can falsely skip a profitable USDC/USDT path.
